{"tid":2124214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"選舉主任要求民主派澄清是否支持國安法、繼續請求美國制裁香港及35+否決預算案","createTime":"2020-07-25T08:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T10:55:52.000Z","uid":59818,"like":17,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"af719fc5633554ffe5f5396c6b868e11fa9d4d9b","tid":2124214,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T08:44:58.000Z","msg":"【最新】至少6名民主派被要求澄清是否效忠特區<br />\n<br />\n公民黨楊岳橋、鄭達鴻、會計界梁繼昌、本土派劉頴匡、區議員袁嘉蔚、梁晃維分別收到選舉主任來信，要求澄清他們的政治立場。<br />\n<br />\n劉頴匡證實收到選舉主任來信，當中問及五條問題，包括是否仍繼續請求美國落實制裁香港、是否反對港區國安法等。<br />\n<br />\n梁繼昌亦向眾新聞證實，收到選舉主任詢問支持35+否決所有政府議案，及是否向美國建議制裁任何香港官員。梁繼昌說兩者皆否，稍後將會公開選舉主任信件及回覆。"},{"pid":"1b24a866fb9d26585f366952ac9887cd9f273e08","tid":2124214,"uid":59818,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T08:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1umiph7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1umiph7.jpg&h=c722e796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/on5nQYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fon5nQYa.jpg&h=61ac1fbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EchxtKS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEchxtKS.jpg&h=31ee7e89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e57a9da9b4e89cbbdc78d33879fd3018ae97eda9","tid":2124214,"uid":274531,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T08:47:35.000Z","msg":"反國安法都問，有咩好講，DQ啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0122242c57346ce7b35659e7801c2a1544015c0a","tid":2124214,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T08:47:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b59ee19b17156c154c8a32655285a44bed3d21b0","tid":2124214,"uid":12404,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T08:48:09.000Z","msg":"啲問題咁撚on9 都問得出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class